and a kiss that made her not dead anymore.

556
00:47:47,080 --> 00:47:48,764
如果你在这里吻她...
If you kiss her here...

557
00:47:48,960 --> 00:47:50,610
她就不会死了
she won't die.

558
00:47:51,280 --> 00:47:52,645
我知道的
I know it.

559
00:47:53,880 --> 00:47:55,086
好吗?
Okay?

560
00:47:56,640 --> 00:47:58,210
快答应
Say okay.

561
00:48:00,640 --> 00:48:01,721
好
Okay.

562
00:48:02,760 --> 00:48:03,886
好的
Okay.

563
00:48:04,120 --> 00:48:06,122
你现在可以把我抱到床上了
You can put me to bed now.

564
00:48:50,640 --> 00:48:52,369
我是帕里・索姆斯
Pearly Soames.

565
00:48:58,520 --> 00:49:00,363
我有预约
I have an appointment.

566
00:49:20,360 --> 00:49:22,169
你好 帕里
Hello, Pearly.

567
00:49:23,280 --> 00:49:26,807
你好 很荣幸来到这 大人
Ah. Hello, Your Honor. Sir.

568
00:49:28,720 --> 00:49:29,926
当然了
Oh, of course.

569
00:49:36,880 --> 00:49:38,484
那个...
Eh...

570
00:49:39,560 --> 00:49:44,202
我来是希望能得到豁免边界限令的特权
I'm here to request special dispensation regarding the boundaries of jurisdiction.

571
00:49:44,400 --> 00:49:45,447
继续说
Proceed.

572
00:49:47,000 --> 00:49:52,325
我想获准进入城北地区 大人
I'd like permission to travel north of the city, Your Honor.

573
00:49:55,080 --> 00:49:58,880
噢 这可有点为难我了 帕里 根据你上次的表现
Wow, that is quite a request, Pearly, considering what happened last time.

574
00:49:59,080 --> 00:50:01,924
噢 那只是个误会
Well, you know, it was a misunderstanding.

575
00:50:02,200 --> 00:50:03,247
是嘛
Yeah.

576
00:50:03,440 --> 00:50:07,081
好吧 小鬼 干脆一次把这事说清楚
Well, demon, let's get this over with.

577
00:50:12,200 --> 00:50:15,647
帕里・索姆斯 作为曼哈顿和第五区的恶魔执行者
Pearly Soames, Warden of Manhattan and the Five Boroughs

578
00:50:15,840 --> 00:50:18,161
