- 糟  - 糟了?
- Uh-oh.  - Uh-oh?

670
00:55:17,200 --> 00:55:19,407
- 不小心  - 不小心?
- Qops.  - Oops?

671
00:56:18,280 --> 00:56:19,725
我轻吗?
Am I light or heavy?

672
00:56:19,920 --> 00:56:22,127
轻得像根羽毛
Light as a feather.

673
00:56:24,640 --> 00:56:26,165
晚安 彼得・雷克
Good night, Peter Lake.

674
00:56:27,200 --> 00:56:28,804
晚安 小维拉
Good night, little Willa.

675
00:56:35,200 --> 00:56:38,044
